            "body": "It looks like neovim can not figure out the correct size your terminal after your resizing operation. I have also seen this on cmder. It may have something to do with your terminal. Because of this, I quit using terminal neovim and use nvim-qt instead, which does not have this issue.\r\n\r\nTry to reduce your setting bit by bit to see if the issue persists, and creating a minimal conf to reproduce would be helpful.",
